Jill Ireland https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jill_Ireland 0 Jill Dorothy Ireland (24 April 1936 – 18 May 1990) was an English actress and singer, best known for her collaborations (totalling fifteen films) with her second husband, Charles Bronson.
